title: Pennsylvania SOS, Obama and McCain votes by county in the 2008 General Election, Pennsylvania, Nov 05, 2008
name: Pennsylvania SOS, Obama and McCain votes by county in the 2008 General Election, Pennsylvania, Nov 05, 2008
description: The poly shapefile shows vote counts and percent share of Obama and McCain by county in Pennsylvania from the 2008 General Election. The original data was downloaded from Pennsylvania Secretary of State website and is uptodate as of 5 AM on 5th November, 2008.
